            "id": "https://ttt.td/2023/02/16/adguardhome-server-filter-china-domain",
            "url": "https://ttt.td/2023/02/16/adguardhome-server-filter-china-domain",
            "title": "使用AdGuardHome搭建私有DNS并对ChinaDomain进行分流",
            "date_published": "2023-02-16T07:15:27.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"使用AdGuardHome自建的DNS服务，并对中国域名指定DNS上游\"><a href=\"#使用AdGuardHome自建的DNS服务，并对中国域名指定DNS上游\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用AdGuardHome自建的DNS服务，并对中国域名指定DNS上游\"></a>使用AdGuardHome自建的DNS服务，并对中国域名指定DNS上游</h2><p>编辑<code>AdGuardHome.yaml</code>设置<code>upstream_dns_file = &quot;/usr/share/adguardhome.upstream&quot;</code>，设置<code>all_servers = true</code>，设置<code>cache_optimistic = true</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://input-s3.mn.input.im/adm-group/1/20230216/63edd8a26bc44.png\" alt=\"AdGuardHome.png\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"搭建自己的无污染的DNS服务器\"><a href=\"#搭建自己的无污染的DNS服务器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建自己的无污染的DNS服务器\"></a>搭建自己的无污染的DNS服务器</h1><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装脚本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">curl -o <span class=\"string\">&quot;/usr/local/bin/upstream.sh&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BigUIFU/AGH_SELF/main/DNS/upsteam.sh&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">chmod</span> +x /usr/local/bin/upstream.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\">/usr/local/bin/upstream.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 创建systemd服务定时更新</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">curl -o <span class=\"string\">&quot;/etc/systemd/system/upstream.service&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BigUIFU/AGH_SELF/main/DNS/upsteam.service&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">curl -o <span class=\"string\">&quot;/etc/systemd/system/upstream.timer&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BigUIFU/AGH_SELF/main/DNS/upsteam.timer&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl daemon-reload</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl <span class=\"built_in\">enable</span> upstream.timer</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl start upstream.timer</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl status upstream</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n",
            "tags": [
                "DNS",
                "Linux"
            ]
        },
        {
